Invocation Name: west ham united songs
des:
West Ham United Songs will bring the song of the London Stadium right to you. Sing along to the famous, "I'm Forever Blowing Bubbles," and get fired up for game day. This skill will warm the hearts of any hammers fan and teach your friends and family the lyric of the old Thames Ironworks Football Club. Come on you irons!

Is it game day? Ask Alexa to open West Ham United Songs and then say, "It's game day!" You will appreciate her response.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
